description:
Smile! Cosmetic dentist Dr. Marc Lowenberg talks about bad breath, which oral care products are B.S., and what you can really do to get a more beautiful smile. Before that, we've got tips for preventing eyeshadow fallout and our take on some fancy new facials. Plus, Jenn talks about bladder matters, including how she deals with interstitial cystitis and recurrent UTIs.

Become a member at https://plus.acast.com/s/fatmascara.
